title: Initial Myocardial Infarction
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts of diagnoses for initial myocardial infarction.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element related to Diagnosis.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that represent an initial diagnosis of myocardial infarction.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that represent subsequent myocardial infarction.)
